rows.label: tlk00040104_msg0001
rows.name:
Punin, what are you doing sneaking
about the place?

rows.label: tlk00040104_msg0003
rows.name:
Never Rex mind about Punin!
What happen to salvaging?
Chairman expect results!

rows.label: tlk00040104_msg0004
rows.name:
Oh don't you worry, I'll be working
very hard. Especially when there's
a 100,000G reward on the line!

rows.label: tlk00040104_msg0005
rows.name:
That the spirit! Now quick-quick!
Hurry down stairs and head to
rendezvous point!
